    "detail": "The room is spacious with good features like a convenience store located within the lobby area. The staff were English-speaking and they provide helpful service in terms of recommendations of where to go in Jeju Island. The location is also superb. It is just 15 minutes away from the airport, 15 minutes walk to the city centre and shopping area, and 10 minutes walk to the seaport where fresh seafood is served. The wind in the area, however, is crazy since the hotel is located beside the sea and unblocked by other buildings. There's also a steady stream of tourists since it's a big hotel. But definitely value for money for family stay.",
